OL,3,CFormer Reform leader in Wales admits
OL,4,Cbribery charges over pro-Russian
OL,5,Cstatements
OL,7,FHe was tasked by Ukrainian Oleg
OL,8,FVoloshyn on at least eight occasions
OL,9,Fto make specific statements in return
OL,10,Ffor money, the court was told.
OL,12,FGill denied one charge of conspiracy
OL,13,Fto commit bribery during a hearing at
OL,14,Fthe Old Bailey on Friday.
