OL,3,CFormer Reform leader in Wales admits
OL,4,Cbribery charges over pro-Russian
OL,5,Cstatements
OL,7,FThey emerged after Gill was stopped at
OL,8,FManchester Airport on September 13
OL,9,F2021 under the Counter Terrorism and
OL,10,FBorder Security Act 2019.
OL,12,FDefence barrister Peter Wright KC
OL,13,Facknowledged Gill was facing a
OL,14,Fsubstantial jail sentence, but asked
OL,15,Ffor bail for the married father-of-
OL,16,Ffive before his next hearing.
OL,18,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb granted
OL,19,Fconditional bail as she set a
OL,20,Fsentencing hearing at the Old Bailey
OL,21,Fon November 21.
